longBusinessSummary: Golden Eagle Retail Group Limited, an investment holding company, develops and operates lifestyle center and stylish department store chain in the People's Republic of China. The company operates through Retail Operations; Property Development and Hotel Operations; and Other Operations segments. It also operates supermarkets and hotels. As of December 31, 2020, the company operated 31 self-owned stores with a total gross floor area of 2,511,058 square meters and a total operating area of 1,709, 571 square meters; and 16 lifestyle centers with a total gross floor area of 1,991,662 square meters in the People's Republic of China. In addition, it engages in trading activities; property holding; operation of aquariums; and trading of cosmetic products. Further, the company is involved in the automobile inspection, sale, distribution, and exhibition; and property development and investment. Additionally, it offers communication and information service, as well as invests in education services. The company was founded in 1995 and is based in Nanjing, the People's Republic of China. Golden Eagle Retail Group Limited is a subsidiary of Golden Eagle International Retail Group Limited.
address2: 17th Floor No. 888 Yingtian Street Jianye District
